數值分析一



















ESS3050 Numerical Analysis I, 數值分析一










Course Description:
            As having been stated in the preface of the text book, the purpose of this course is "to introduce morden approximation techniques; to explain how, why, and when they can be expected to work; and to provide a foundation for further study of numerical analysis and scientific computing"
             




課程說明：
            求多項式與超越方程式之根、解聯立方程式、解特徵值問題、曲線配合、數值微 分與積分、解常微分方程。 












